Developer's Data Retention and Deletion Policy
As part of our commitment to user privacy and security, we enforce a strict data retention and deletion policy for the "Happening Now" application. This policy outlines how we handle the storage and removal of user data, ensuring compliance with privacy laws and regulations.
Data Retention
We retain personal data only for as long as necessary to provide the services requested by the user, to comply with our legal obligations, to resolve disputes, and to enforce our agreements. The retention period for different types of data may vary depending on the nature of the data and the purposes for which it is processed.
Data Deletion
Users have the right to request the deletion of their personal data. Upon request, we will delete or anonymize your personal data from our databases, except where retention is required by law, regulation, or to protect the safety, security, and integrity of our services
